    <string name="privacy_policy_content">Privacy Policy\n\nLast updated: 2024\n\n1. Data Collection\nThis app does NOT collect, transmit, or share any personal data. All notes are stored entirely on your device using a local Room database.\n\n2. Permissions\nThis app uses minimal permissions: biometric authentication (optional, for note locking), alarm scheduling (for reminders), and notifications (for reminder alerts). No internet permission is required.\n\n3. Local Storage Only\nAll notes are stored in a secure local database on your Android device. Only you have access to your notes.\n\n4. Third-Party Services\nThis app uses no analytics, advertising, or tracking services of any kind.\n\n5. Your Rights\nSince no data leaves your device, you have complete control. You can delete all data by clearing the app or uninstalling it.\n\nContact us through the Play Store listing with any questions.</string>
