    <string name="terms_content">Terms and Conditions\n\nLast updated: 2024\n\n1. Acceptance\nBy using this app, you agree to these Terms.\n\n2. License\nWe grant a personal, non-commercial license to use this app.\n\n3. User Content\nYou own all notes and data you create. We have no access to it.\n\n4. Disclaimer\nThis app is provided as-is. We are not liable for data loss. Back up important notes using the built-in Backup feature.\n\n5. Updates\nWe may update the app and these terms. Continued use constitutes acceptance.\n\n6. Governing Law\nGoverned by applicable local laws.\n\nThank you for using Notepad++ – Smart Notes.</string>
